  "response": "As of my last update, some of the best in-ear earphones available in India under \u20b9500, known for their sound quality, include:\n\n1. **Mi Earphones Basic**:\n   - Known for their decent sound quality, comfortable fit, and durability. They also come with a three-button remote for controlling music and calls.\n\n2. **Realme Buds 2**:\n   - Offers good bass and overall sound quality. They come with a tangle-free cable and an inline microphone. Note that prices can sometimes go slightly above \u20b9500 during sales.\n\n3. **Redmi Earphones**:\n   - Similar in quality to Mi earphones, they provide a balanced sound profile and come with a built-in microphone.\n\n4. **Boat Bassheads 100**:\n   - Popular for their bass-heavy sound signature, these earphones are stylish and come with an inline mic.\n\n5. **Zebronics Zeb-Rush**:\n   - Features a decent audio profile and a comfortable fit, along with an in-line mic for calls.\n\nWhen choosing earphones at this price point, it\u2019s important to consider the fit and comfort, as well as user reviews about durability. Prices and availability can vary, so it's worth checking online platforms and local stores for the best deals.",
